data.description: Custom lakefront property with private dock nestled at the end of Journeys End. Stunning views are everyday at this one of a kind house. You will want to end every night watching the sunset on the lake. With an open floor plan with large wood double hung windows, heart pine flooring, and wood trim, this house is made to entertain. Custom reclaimed cypress trim encompasses the bottom half of the home. The house has three large covered porches, two face Lake Iamonia, with a deck large enough to entertain. Other features include a hot tub, basement, and large utility room with half bath. The ground level master suite has heart pine floors, a wall of windows facing the lake, and sitting area. The first floor also includes a large breakfast area, guest bedroom and bath, and formal dining room or game room. The second floor has two bedrooms with dormer seats, home office/loft, bonus room and walk in attic.
